external-data-source: Error, one of the following options is required, --install|--start|--stop|--postprocess

The following options are available:
	--install                 install this perf tool

	--start|stop|postprocess  start/stop/post-process the data collection
	--dir=str                 directory to store data collection (required)
	--type=str                the type of the external data source (required, currently only "url" is supported)
	--source=str              the only supported "type" of external data source currently is "url", to which one
	                          provides the URL for the data source via "--source" parameter (required)
